    "featureBullets": [
      "Bare With Me Makeup Foundation: Achieve an instantly smooth and blurred complexion with our first blurring skin tint foundation. In buildable, medium coverage matte foundation finish shades formulated to enhance your own skin color and tone",
      "\"No Filter Needed\" Foundation Makeup: Treat your skin with skincare infused face makeup with Glycerin, Matcha and Niacinamide for visibly even, radiant and healthy-looking skin. Blurred finish feels lightweight on skin and provides 12HR hydration",
      "Face From Foundation To Finish: Complete your makeup look with our full line of face products to aid in color correction and coverage from concealer, blush, bronzer, foundations and contouring to palettes and powders",
      "Cruelty Free Cosmetics: We believe animals belong in our arms, not in a lab, All of our makeup is certified and acknowledged by PETA as a cruelty free brand, We don't test any of our products on animals",
      "Discover NYX Professional Makeup: Try all of our professional makeup products today from eyeshadow, eyeliner, and false lashes to liquid lipstick, lip gloss, primer, concealer, setting sprays and eyebrow makeup"
    ],
    "description": "Skip the IG-filter. Introducing NYX Professional Makeup Bare With Me Blur Tint Foundation, the first blurring skin tint that blurs it all. Imperfections? BLURRED. Pores? BLURRED. Discoloration? BLURRED. Texture? BLURRED. Achieve instantly smooth filter-like blurred skin in 24 diverse shades, formulated to enhance your color and tone. Medium buildable coverage with a matte blurred finish that feels lightweight on skin and provides 12h hydration. Formulated with Glycerin, Matcha and Niacinamide for a skin so smooth, no filter needed. Use the Bare With Me Blur Tint Foundation Brush to buff the product all over face for an even streak-free blurred finish. Feel free to layer for fuller coverage. Use a small amount of product, a little goes a long way.",
