      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Smooth coverage, hydrating, good color match",
          "reviewText": "Nyx had a Bare With Me lightweight tinted hydrator/foundation years ago that I loved, and I've always been kind of searching for an equivalent to it ever since it was discontinued. This one comes close, but is still a little bit heavier than I normally prefer for everyday wear. Still, it has good coverage, looks dewy/moist without being greasy or heavy, and matches well. I have a light/neutral skin tone that can be tricky to get right. Overall, I recommend this foundation",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2026",
          "customer": "ARW",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEIULBRHI23X66ZIRT5VNHM26IAQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
