            "size": "1.01 Fl Oz (Pack of 1)"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "3 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Light and refreshing a little goes a long way!\ud83d\ude42",
          "reviewText": "What I liked about the product was there\u2019s a lot of coverage with a little amount. My first time trying this and as an older woman people say you can\u2019t wear a liquid foundation, but I\u2019ve always been wearing it and this is incredible! I put a little under my eyes and it went a long way. I actually added on my cheeks as well just a dab maybe the size of a green pee over my nose my eyes I usually use my make up brush, but I was just curious how it was going to match my skin tone and it was perfect just perfect and it is lightweight. It looks nice on my skin, but I got it in the evening so tomorrow I\u2019m going to try it close to the window so I can doublecheck . But right now I\u2019m liking what I bought! Mine is light medium number 09",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2025",
          "customer": "Sharon M.",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHAG3G3YMSFZSCUCJBJIPURYJGQQ",
